{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator/build-an-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator","demoType":null,"title":"Izračunavanje zbora neobičnih Fibonaccijevih brojeva","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom laboratoriju ćete napraviti kalkulator za zbir Fibonaccijevih brojeva koji računa zbir svih Fibonaccijevih brojeva manjih ili jednakih datom pozitivnom broju.</p>\n<p><strong>Cilj</strong>: Popunite korisničke priče navedene ispod i prođite sve testove kako biste završili laboratoriju.</p>\n<p><strong>Priče korisnika:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Trebalo bi da postoji funkcija <code>sumFibs</code> koja prima broj kao argument.</li>\n<li>Funkcija <code>sumFibs</code> treba da vrati sumu svih neparnih brojeva Fibonaccija koji su manji ili jednaki datoj broju.</li>\n<li>Fibonacci niz počinje sa <code>0</code> i <code>1</code>, a svaki sledeći broj je zbir dva prethodna broja.</li>\n<li>Samo neparni brojevi Fibonaccija će biti dodati u sumu.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"a5229172f011153519423690","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-fundamentals-review","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator/build-an-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš funkciju <code>sumFibs</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(sumFibs);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(1)</code> trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(sumFibs(1));"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(1000)</code> treba da vrati <code>1785</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumFibs(1000), 1785);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(4000000)</code> treba da vrati <code>4613732</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumFibs(4000000), 4613732);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(4)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>5</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumFibs(4), 5);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(75024)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>60696</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumFibs(75024), 60696);"},{"text":"<p><code>sumFibs(75025)</code> treba da vrati <code>135721</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(sumFibs(75025), 135721);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/#lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator","dashedName":"build-an-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator","certification":"javascript-fundamentals-review","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-fundamentals-review","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/lab-element-skipper/implement-an-element-skipper","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/lab-html-entitiy-converter/implement-an-html-entity-converter","id":"a5229172f011153519423690","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function sumFibs(num) {\r\n  let a = 0, b = 1;\r\n  let sum = 0;\r\n\r\n  while (b <= num) {\r\n    if (b % 2 !== 0) {\r\n      sum += b;\r\n    }\r\n    [a, b] = [b, a + b];\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  return sum;\r\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-fundamentals-review/lab-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator/build-an-odd-fibonacci-sum-calculator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}